<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<ScrollView xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
    android:id="@+id/ScrollView01"
    android:fillViewport="false">

    <LinearLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
        xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools" android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="match_parent" android:paddingLeft="@dimen/activity_horizontal_margin"
        android:paddingRight="@dimen/activity_horizontal_margin"
        android:paddingTop="@dimen/activity_vertical_margin"
        android:paddingBottom="@dimen/activity_vertical_margin"
        android:background="@drawable/bg1"
        tools:context="com.example.sudhanshumishra.astrovision.Aries"
        android:orientation="vertical"
        >


        <LinearLayout
            android:layout_width="350dp"
            android:layout_height="1440dp"
            android:weightSum="1"
            android:orientation="vertical"
            >

            <TextView
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="110dp"
                android:text="ARIES"
                android:textSize="70dp"
                android:textStyle="bold"
                android:textAlignment="center"
                />

            <ImageView
                android:layout_width="310dp"
                android:layout_height="250dp"
                android:background="@drawable/aries" />


            <HorizontalScrollView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                <TextView
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="700dp"

                    android:layout_marginTop="15dp"
                    android:textColor="#FFFF66"
                    android:text="Strengths:\n
- Independent\n
- Generous\n
- Optimistic\n
- Enthusiastic\n
- Courageous\n\n

Weakness:\n
- Moody\n
- Short tempered\n
- Self-involved\n
- Impulsive\n
- Impatient\n\n

As the first sign in the zodiac, the presence of \n
Aries almost always marks the beginning of something\n
energetic and turbulent..They are continuously looking\n
for dynamic, speed and competition. They are always first\n
in everything - from work to social gatherings. Thanks to\n
its ruling planet Mars, Aries is one of the most active zodiac \n
signs. People born under the Aries sign, are meant to emphasize\n
the search for answers to personal and metaphysical questions.\n
This is the biggest feature of this incarnation.\n
Aries is a fire sign, just like Leo and Sagittarius.\n
This means that it is in their nature to take action,\n
sometimes before they think about it well. Their fiery \n
ruler affects their excellent organizational skills, so \n
you'll rarely meet an Aries who doesn't like to finish \n
more things at once, often even before the lunch break! \n
The challenges are increased when they are impatient, \n
aggressive and vent anger on others.

"/>
            </HorizontalScrollView>
            <TextView
                android:layout_width="350dp"
                android:layout_height="60dp"
                android:id="@+id/tv_luck"
                android:textColor="#FFFF66"
                />

            <EditText
                android:layout_width="320dp"
                android:layout_height="150dp"
                android:background="#FAD7A0"
                android:textColorHint="#A569BD"
                android:id="@+id/edt_msg"
                />

            <Button
                android:layout_width="90dp"
                android:layout_height="60dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="140dp"
                android:text="call"
                android:onClick="callme"
                />
            <Button
                android:layout_width="90dp"
                android:layout_height="60dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="140dp"
                android:text="sms"
                android:onClick="send"
                />

        </LinearLayout>


        <LinearLayout
            android:layout_width="350dp"
            android:layout_height="60dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="30dp"
            >

            <Button
                android:layout_width="120dp"
                android:layout_height="60dp"
                android:text="Sign Out"
                android:textStyle="bold"
                android:textSize="10dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="120dp"
                android:onClick="signout"
                />
        </LinearLayout>

    </LinearLayout>
</ScrollView>
